OL,3,CPedestrian in her 70s dies following
OL,4,Ccrash in Cockermouth
OL,6,FPolice are investigating the collision
OL,7,Fwhich occurred just after 9pm on
OL,8,FSaturday night.
OL,10,FThe incident between a pedestrian in
OL,11,Fher 70s add a car, driven by a man in
OL,12,Fis 30s, happened on Lamplugh Road in
OL,13,FCockermouth.
OL,15,FOfficers say the driver is assisting
OL,16,Fthem with their investigation.
OL,18,FThe road was closed for a number of
OL,19,Fhours whilst a forensic collision
OL,20,Finvestigation was carried out.
