OL,3,CPedestrian in her 70s dies following
OL,4,Ccrash in Cockermouth
OL,6,FAnyone with any information is asked
OL,7,Fto contact Cumbria Police - which can
OL,8,Fbe done either online or by phone.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Cumbria Police
OL,11,Fsaid, "The collision occurred at
OL,12,F9.09pm yesterday (March 14). The
OL,13,Fpedestrian, a woman in her 70s, sadly
OL,14,Fdied at the scene.
OL,16,F"Anyone with information relating to
OL,17,Fthis incident can report online at
OL,18,Fhttps://orlo.uk/cJiui, quoting
OL,19,Fincident number 226 of 14 March 2026.
OL,20,FYou can also phone on 101.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
